==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pendragon
<hw>Pen"drag*on</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A chief leader or
a king; a head; a dictator; -- a title assumed by the ancient British
chiefs when called to lead other chiefs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The dread <qex>Pendragon</qex>, Britain's king of kings.</q>
<rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pendular</ent>⟦br⟧
